flowchart TD
    START([🧍 Customer Arrives at Outlet]) --> MODE{Pickup or Return?}

    %% ─── PICKUP BRANCH ───
    MODE -->|PICKUP| P1[Greet customer &\nask for Booking Reference]
    P1 --> P2[Search booking in system\nby Booking Ref or Name]
    P2 --> P3{Booking found\n& status = confirmed?}
    P3 -->|No| P3N[Check if booking exists\nunder different name/phone]
    P3N --> P3N2{Found?}
    P3N2 -->|No| P3X[❌ Cannot proceed\nContact manager]
    P3N2 -->|Yes| P4
    P3 -->|Yes| P4[Verify customer identity\nIC / Passport]
    P4 --> P5{ID matches\nbooking?}
    P5 -->|No| P5N[❌ Reject pickup\nID mismatch — inform customer]
    P5 -->|Yes| P6[Collect payment:\n• Remaining rental fee\n• RM200 security deposit]
    P6 --> P7[Print / show agreement\nfor customer to sign]
    P7 --> P8[Prepare camera unit:\n• Check condition\n• Format memory card\n• Charge battery]
    P8 --> P9[Hand over camera &\nexplain basic usage]
    P9 --> P10[Mark booking as ACTIVE\nin system — records pickup time]
    P10 --> P11[✅ Pickup Complete\nWish customer happy shooting!]

    %% ─── RETURN BRANCH ───
    MODE -->|RETURN| R1[Ask for Booking Reference\nor customer name]
    R1 --> R2[Search booking in system]
    R2 --> R3[Receive camera\nfrom customer]
    R3 --> R4[Inspect camera condition:\n• Physical damage?\n• All accessories returned?\n• Memory card included?]
    R4 --> R5{Any damage\nor missing items?}
    R5 -->|Yes| R6[Document damage\nwith photos in system]
    R6 --> R7[Inform customer of\ndeduction from deposit]
    R7 --> R8[Calculate deduction\n& refund balance]
    R5 -->|No| R9[Full RM200 deposit\nrefunded to customer]
    R8 --> R10[Mark booking as RETURNED\nin system]
    R9 --> R10
    R10 --> R11[✅ Return Complete\nThank customer!]

